text.section:
The County Mayor or the Mayor's designee will assign staff to support the work of the Council and its committees as follows:
Providing minutes of all meetings;
Preparing the meeting agendas, in coordination with the Chairperson and/or Committee Chairperson(s);
Providing for the notification of all meetings and for the public notices of such meetings;
Arranging meeting locations and materials for distribution;
Preparing and distributing materials of an informative nature to each member;
Giving a staff report on relevant activities; and
Act as the research and clerical arm of the Council and committees, subject to limitation of available resources from Miami-Dade County.
